text: Kerbal Space Program 2 is a space flight simulation video game. It is a sequel to Kerbal Space Program, and was released into early access on February 24th, 2023. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:2023 video games Category:Construction and management simulation games Category:Early access video games Category:Open-world video games Category:Science fiction video games Category:Single-player video games Category:Video game sequels Category:Video games about extraterrestrial life Category:Video games developed in the United States Category:Windows games
